descriptionHtml:
You are a young wizard, traveling the world you destroy evil spirits.
Only in your power to save this world. On your way you will meet a variety of enemies: swordsmen, magicians, monsters. But you are not a bastard, you become stronger, buy new staves and pump your skills.
The world rely on you!
